---
title: Beef Rissoles & Beetroot Relish with Cheesy Fries, Pear Salad & BBQ Mayo
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing winner, but when you cover them with sweet beetroot relish and smokey BBQ mayo, they’re even
harder to refuse! This colourful plate also gets a serve of cheesy fries and a fresh pear salad for a dinner filled with delights.
